title: Every Item In An Air Force Gunship Pilot's Go Bag | Loadout | Insider Business
description:
Maj. Riley Feeney breaks down every item a pilot carries in their go bag, including night-vision goggles, an iPad, and their helmet. Feeney explains why each item is integral for each flight. The AC-130J is retrofitted with a precision-weapons package and is able to aid in missions like close air support, air interdiction, and armed reconnaissance.

00:11: Helmet
00:59: Lip light
01:42: Night-vision goggles
03:06: Electronic flight bag

05:20: Sunglasses
06:02: Dog tags
06:33: Earplugs
07:23: Water bottle
07:51: Gum
